<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3482:3509'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '002-11b' );" name="002-11b" class="pb">[002-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3509:3532'>展衣色白后以禮見王及賔客之服佩綬如上上首服</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3532:3555'>亦編白屨黒絇繶純後鄭云展當為襢者案喪大記云</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='3555:3578'>世婦襢衣襢之言亶也亶誠也案詩鄘風君子偕老及</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='3578:3601'>此文皆作展並是正經鄭必讀為襢者以襢從衣而有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='3601:3624'>衣義爾雅亶展雖同訓為誠展者言之誠亶者行之誠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='3624:3647'>貴行賤言襢字以亶為聲有行誠之義故從襢也此亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='3647:3670'>卿大夫之妻從夫助君祭宗廟得服之案祭義曰君牽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='3670:3693'>牲夫人奠盎君獻尸夫人薦豆卿大夫相君命婦相夫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='3693:3720'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '002-12a' );" name="002-12a" class="pb">[002-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='3720:3725'>人是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='3725:3752'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '002-13a' );" name="002-13a" class="pb">[002-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
