<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='4357:4360'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='4360:4363'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='4363:4390'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '002-15b' );" name="002-15b" class="pb">[002-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='4390:4413'>纁衻當嫁之女所服也士昬禮云女次純衣纁衻立于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='4413:4436'>房中南面注云次首飾今之髲也周禮追師掌為副編</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='4436:4460'>次純衣絲衣也此衣亦𤣥色衻縁也衻之為言任也以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='4460:4483'>纁縁其絲衣象隂氣上任於陽也取交接有依之義凡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='4483:4506'>婦人不常施衻之衣盛昬禮為此服耳喪大記曰復不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='4506:4529'>以衻明非常衣也詩武王女下嫁齊侯之子車服不繫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='4529:4551'>其夫下王后一等乗厭翟服褕翟加纁衻首飾亦副</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='4551:4578'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0078', 'WYG', '002-16a' );" name="002-16a" class="pb">[002-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
